        <abstract> 
<p>William Clowes [printer for J. Murray] estimates that <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi> will come to a first volume of 648 pages and a second volume of 624 pages – which is too much for volumes the same size as <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>. Murray proposes a larger size.</p> 
